{
  "stem": "19055.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 498.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The adults were hollering through that little opening, water, water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Please give us some water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt like Quasimodo when he's asking for water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that peasant would look up with his shovel in his hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, hey, Jew?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Do you have a gold watch?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Throw me a gold watch, I give you some water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's a picture I still see very sharply if, if I had taken a photograph.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the train went by.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it went ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And eventually, we, we arrived to Austria, as I learned later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was another camp.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was called Strasshof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The train stopped a screeching halt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they evacuated us before [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] a German SS came from boxcar to boxcar with a bowl and said, you give me all your valuables.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Otherwise, you'll be shot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So everybody gave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody took any risk to keep anything, not even a, not even a ring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I told you before that I would trade my sandwiches for my stamp collection.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I took out my stamp, stamp collection.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I threw it in his bowl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "To me, that was more than a, a, a diamond ring or, or gold necklace or anything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "To me, that was my jewelry, my valuable, the most valuable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And even years after, I was thinking of this stamp collection.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And, and I really never took, took on again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we arrived to Strasshof.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they disinfected us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You had to undress and go through all sorts of examinations, naked men and naked women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And doctors checked us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we stayed there I think two days or three days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was an organized camp, in order to distribute people from these different areas.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
